text: HVF may refer to: * HVF, station code for Haverfordwest railway station, in Wales * Heavy Vehicles Factory, an Indian defence company * Les Herbiers VF, a French football club * Hillary Victory Fund, an American political fundraising organization * HVF may refer to Hidden Vale Farm, a company in PNW, USA that produces all natural, handmade beeswax skin care products.
title: HVF
